func (ci geo_s2_CellID) lsb() uint64 { return uint64(ci) & -uint64(ci) }

func (ci geo_s2_CellID) Children() [4]geo_s2_CellID {
	var ch [4]geo_s2_CellID
	lsb := geo_s2_CellID(ci.lsb())
	ch[0] = ci - lsb + lsb>>2
	lsb >>= 1
	ch[1] = ch[0] + lsb
	ch[2] = ch[1] + lsb
	ch[3] = ch[2] + lsb
	return ch
}
